{
  "stem": "1183.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Another incident was that a boy was stepping on my finger and broke my nail, totally crushed it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He just ignored it, and I had to wait till it was recess or when we went to home-- went home to let it look after.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Otherwise, I learned and I completed that public school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I didn't mind that much, except from him, but it was normal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Then in 1940, I was 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I graduated from public school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I entered the Jewish-- and I entered the public high school, where I did fairly well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And that was already in 1940.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "During the time in May 1940, there was the invasion of the Germans in Holland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Naturally, we knew about that, because we read the papers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And in September '39, we followed that, and Germany invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And then they came closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Then one night, just the night before, my parents were discussing maybe we should move to America.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "It was just the night before on the 9th of May, during the night we woke up with a terrific noise, and we heard all of the airplanes coming over.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And all the people we were-- our bedroom was close to around them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "We were standing outside at 3 o'clock during the night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And we are looking at the sky, and the sky was black from all the German planes invading Holland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there's lots of excitement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time nobody yet felt anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans were pretty clever to wait with all actions what they were planning to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Life afterwards, I went to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And life resembled-- remained or returned to, not say normal, but to almost normal.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
